課程概述 Course Description
       本課程是老年醫學與健康照護的基本概念入門，主要包括老化與長壽的科學新知、老年人的疾病預防與健康促進相關之知識、老年醫學評估原則、老年病癥候群的評估、處置和預防，以及老年照護相關的倫理與法律問題。This class introduces the basic concept of geriatric medicine and elderly health care, including basics of aging and longevity, disease prevention and health promotion in the elderly, principles of geriatric assessment, assessment and management of geriatric syndromes, and ethical and legal issues of elderly care.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
幫助學生熟悉老年醫學與健康照護領域的基本概念瞭解常見的老年疾病及症狀的評估、處置和預防學習與各種不同領域專業人員合作之運作模式 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Approach and communication with the elderly.2Overview of geriatric medicine.3Secrets of aging and longevity in humans
Biological, laboratory and clinical basis of aging.4Health education and exercise in the elderly/Preventive care and health promotion in the elderly .5Comprehensive geriatric assessment.promotion in the elderly .6Depression and anxiety in the elderly.7Cognitive impairment.8期中考9Nutritional problems in the elderly.Urinary incontinence./Urinary incontinence.10Osteoporosis.11Pharmacology and prescription for the elderly.Falls in the elderly.12Immobility, frailty and failure to thrive in the elderly.13Principles of rehabilitation in the elderly.14Long-term care and quality assessment.15Palliative medicine .16Abuse and neglect in the elderly.Ethical and legal issues in geriatric care.17期末考18期末考 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


